parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy incorrectly, leading to serious injury or death to the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to a recall and not a specific failure symptom.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or death to the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag failed to deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries to the occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of available parts for the recall repair can lead to a delay in fixing the safety issue, putting vehicle occupants at risk of injury or death.
symptoms: Dealerships are unable to perform the recall repair due to a lack of available parts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unstable brake performance can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the vehicle's inability to stop or slow down properly.
symptoms: The brakes slip or feel soft
the vehicle creeps forward while stopped
the vehicle rolls backward while parked on an incline
the brake pedal has to be gradually depressed to stop the vehicle
the vehicle seizes or throws the driver forward when braking
loud abnormal noises are present when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning ABS system can cause the vehicle to slip or lose control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The vehicle slips or slides when braking
the brakes pulse or vibrate
the vehicle moves forward after coming to a complete stop
the ABS system engages unnecessarily.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty brake pedal can lead to accidents or near-misses due to the driver's inability to stop the vehicle properly.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal has to be pressed almost to the floor to stop the vehicle
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the horn to malfunction, which is a safety hazard, and potentially affect airbag deployment.
symptoms: The horn does not work
the clock spring needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack preload spring can cause the steering wheel to shutter or vibrate at high speeds, which can lead to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel shutters or vibrates at high speeds
despite replacing tires
alignment
and balancing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate fuel economy reading can lead to unexpected fuel consumption, which can cause inconvenience and financial loss.
symptoms: The on-board computer displays inaccurate fuel mileage
the vehicle does not achieve the advertised fuel economy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defect in the steering wheel can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The steering wheel splits at the bottom.
